    "description": "<br><br>精准与快速并存的抓钩平台游戏，这就是《纳齐斯的遗骸(Remnants of Naezith)》。<br><br>优秀的角色操控，无拘无束的移动，没有限制的速度。在这款游戏中，你将会体会精准抓钩与极限速度紧密结合的乐趣与刺激。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/1e9753313b760a553d0ba8afa812e30a.poster.avif?t=1726653354\" width=630 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/1e9753313b760a553d0ba8afa812e30a.webm?t=1726653354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/1e9753313b760a553d0ba8afa812e30a.mp4?t=1726653354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中你将扮演凯拉，一名被古代巨龙纳齐斯所驱使的人类。身负巨龙赐予他的力量，凯拉将摧毁纳齐斯的遗骸，阻止邪恶力量获得这些充满魔力的龙骨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/2ba122857bb657f90c59abbb86ba0945.poster.avif?t=1726653354\" width=630 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/2ba122857bb657f90c59abbb86ba0945.webm?t=1726653354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590590/extras/2ba122857bb657f90c59abbb86ba0945.mp4?t=1726653354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>关卡选择</strong><br>探索四个章节，每章都有具备不同分支的20个关卡。<br></li><li><strong>隐藏关卡</strong><br>找到隐藏的遗骸来解锁特殊关卡。<br></li><li><strong>排行榜</strong><br>观看其他玩家的录像并精进自己的技巧。<br></li><li><strong>全球排行</strong><br>与全球的玩家竞争并获得属于你的奖章。<br></li><li><strong>幽灵</strong><br>和其他玩家或自己最好的成绩进行赛跑。<br></li><li><strong>竞速模式</strong><br>尝试一次性速通游戏内各个章节或全部的关卡。<br></li><li><strong>自定义关卡</strong><br>探索由社区玩家制作的优秀关卡并上传你的关卡。</li></ul>",
